## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent biases present in opinion-based sources. Additionally, the ethical considerations of animal testing are subjective and can vary significantly across different cultural and regulatory contexts. The report relies on secondary sources, which may not capture the full scope of scientific advancements in alternative testing methods.